# Per-developer overrides for the spec-kit-jira extension (custom field
# overrides, alternate project keys, etc.) — never commit. The shared
# config (jira-config.yml) and discovered-fields.json ARE committed so the
# whole team conforms to the same JIRA mappings.
.specify/extensions/jira/jira-config.local.yml

# SpecKit feature.json represents the source of truth for which feature is active.
# Each branch should update this to point to the relevant feature directory,
# but these changes should never be committed as they are specific to the local development environment and would cause problems when merging branches.
.specify/feature.json

# Claude Code per-developer settings. The shared allowlist lives in
# .claude/settings.json (committed); local approvals land here and are personal.
.claude/settings.local.json